4991eefd-feb8-4b75-943b-9db25e499959.title: Cooking tutor
4991eefd-feb8-4b75-943b-9db25e499959.text:
Hello there! Are you interested in hearing all about
cooking?

options.text: How can I train my cooking?
What kinds of things can I cook?

6e733f60-5129-4141-839c-30eeb411b245.title: Cooking tutor
6e733f60-5129-4141-839c-30eeb411b245.text:
Well, just come back any time you want to know how
to cook up a storm!

b92ae923-1d92-4af6-b9a0-ed64b21049d2.title: <player>
b92ae923-1d92-4af6-b9a0-ed64b21049d2.text: How can I train my cooking?

66c863a9-808b-46da-83c3-255b3ec139f2.title: Cooking tutor
66c863a9-808b-46da-83c3-255b3ec139f2.text:
The simplest thing to cook is raw meat or fish. Shrimp
can be caught south of here, to the east of Lumbridge
Swamp. You could ask the fishing tutor for a net if you
have not got one.

be0ceca4-0928-45c9-a0dd-7ed9455d2ef3.title: Cooking tutor
be0ceca4-0928-45c9-a0dd-7ed9455d2ef3.text:
Alternatively, you could acquire some raw beef or
chicken. You can find cows and chickens north of here.
Go over the bridge then follow the path north, you can't
miss them!

58d892dd-8cf4-4c10-9868-e6a2b5063705.text:
When you have a full inventory of meat or fish, find a
range. Look for this icon on your minimap.

2be31715-a670-4399-b5af-5f92b95178ba.title: Cooking tutor
2be31715-a670-4399-b5af-5f92b95178ba.text: You could use my range here if you like.

98646021-bf38-4e8d-bb78-50912d5b7c8f.title: Cooking tutor
98646021-bf38-4e8d-bb78-50912d5b7c8f.text:
Alternatively, you can use your own fire, but it's not as
effective and the food will burn more frequently. To
make a fire, use a tinderbox on some logs.

9cb0dcea-46ef-4a33-bb37-c667f8000248.title: Cooking tutor
9cb0dcea-46ef-4a33-bb37-c667f8000248.text:
Once you've found your range or fire, use your raw
food on it. This will bring up a menu of the food you
can cook. Then select the food you want.

5802afde-3690-480c-a73a-92c90a9fc029.title: Cooking tutor
5802afde-3690-480c-a73a-92c90a9fc029.text:
When you have a full inventory of cooked food, drop
the useless burnt food and find a bank.

08c95341-3285-48a2-a0bd-f40969ab567f.text:
Look for this symbol on your minimap after climbing the
stairs of the Lumbridge Castle to the top. There are
numerous banks around the world, all marked with that
symbol.

840620f1-bace-45be-8f17-477ee019c0a1.title: Cooking tutor
840620f1-bace-45be-8f17-477ee019c0a1.text:
If you're interested in quests, I heard my friend the
cook in Lumbridge Castle is in need of a hand. Just
talk to him and he'll set you off.

e8941c8b-f73d-4c46-80f7-ffba3fa23ce3.title: Cooking tutor
e8941c8b-f73d-4c46-80f7-ffba3fa23ce3.text: Is there anything else you want to know?

29ec8989-35ac-435f-8b8f-c961a6d8de0d.title: <player>
29ec8989-35ac-435f-8b8f-c961a6d8de0d.text: What kinds of things can I cook?

cab72153-9179-4303-896b-269a523a6a27.title: Cooking tutor
cab72153-9179-4303-896b-269a523a6a27.text:
Many things! You can cook anything from fish to
poultry. You could try your hand at making baked
potatoes or even brew some of the good stuff.

70aab96c-e9c7-4a12-9b88-e14b8ace774b.title: Cooking tutor
70aab96c-e9c7-4a12-9b88-e14b8ace774b.text: What would you like to hear about?

options.text: Tell me about Fish and Meat.
Tell me about Pies and Pizzas.

73d2c931-9883-46ea-98d4-5322e850997a.title: <player>
73d2c931-9883-46ea-98d4-5322e850997a.text: Tell me about Fish and Meat.

e342789c-e45b-4a20-abcc-72c292c5dc74.title: Cooking tutor
e342789c-e45b-4a20-abcc-72c292c5dc74.text:
Fish and meat of most varieties can be cooked very
simply on either a fire or range, experiment which one
works for you.

ae8331f2-bc84-4a4c-a6c3-5fd513737a75.title: Cooking tutor
ae8331f2-bc84-4a4c-a6c3-5fd513737a75.text:
You might find that when killing monsters, they drop
some raw meat for you to cook.

b4141f8e-cd26-4f5d-b4e7-6ca72e2bb9a1.title: Cooking tutor
b4141f8e-cd26-4f5d-b4e7-6ca72e2bb9a1.text:
Some of them might have hidden properties. Such as
anglerfish, but you will find it hard getting hold of any
of them at this time.

e0b32c16-93b0-4a5d-b72c-22a9ec527d3a.title: Cooking tutor
e0b32c16-93b0-4a5d-b72c-22a9ec527d3a.text:
Most of the time, cooking meat and fish requires
nothing else but a range or fire. More complicated
dishes might require specialized equipment.

67e3d126-dffe-4f78-b316-82e36c042362.title: Cooking tutor
67e3d126-dffe-4f78-b316-82e36c042362.text:
Would you like to hear about anything else I
mentioned?

54416a8b-f88c-4ec3-b5e3-6dca9797655f.title: Cooking tutor
54416a8b-f88c-4ec3-b5e3-6dca9797655f.text:
You can brew your own beers using the fermenting
vats in either Keldagrim or Port Phasmatys.

a280035d-b705-46ea-9d06-a397fe36fbd8.title: Cooking tutor
a280035d-b705-46ea-9d06-a397fe36fbd8.text:
You might find it hard getting to these places but you
can always buy beer at any pub. Some pubs sell unique
beers too.

12ca2b7f-51ae-4651-92e6-f04d6cb523f8.title: Cooking tutor
12ca2b7f-51ae-4651-92e6-f04d6cb523f8.text:
Baked potatoes are a more advanced food and are
healthy too!

3649b8bf-321a-464a-8dc7-28b76185ac41.title: Cooking tutor
3649b8bf-321a-464a-8dc7-28b76185ac41.text:
They require many different ingredients to make, such
as butter and vegetables, but you will find it hard to
acquire the ingredients needed.

f83070d8-a8f8-4dad-abef-68d7a3be7f27.title: <player>
f83070d8-a8f8-4dad-abef-68d7a3be7f27.text: Tell me about Pies and Pizzas.

5b131dcb-cb5b-49f6-a093-7643148003be.title: Cooking tutor
5b131dcb-cb5b-49f6-a093-7643148003be.text:
Use a pot of flour with a bucket of water. Yo uwill then
need to make some pastry dough.

9986aac3-7c88-44bb-bb9b-8678e144b76d.title: Cooking tutor
9986aac3-7c88-44bb-bb9b-8678e144b76d.text:
Use the patry dough with a pie dish to get a pie shell,
then add your choice of filling such as apples or red
berries.

470f38eb-7058-41f7-a7c1-7b73b9725bea.title: Cooking tutor
470f38eb-7058-41f7-a7c1-7b73b9725bea.text:
Finally cook your pie by using the unbaked pie on a
cooking range. Mmmm...pie.

5227a54b-25cf-44bb-880f-e2eff7f178a4.title: Cooking tutor
5227a54b-25cf-44bb-880f-e2eff7f178a4.text:
Next, we have pizza. You will first need to make
yourself a pizza base, use a pot of flour with a bucket
of water and make a pizza base.

dc745d7e-74f5-484c-ab7d-1427e11ada38.title: Cooking tutor
dc745d7e-74f5-484c-ab7d-1427e11ada38.text:
Now you will need to get yourself a tomato and some
cheese. Use the tomato on the pizza base and then use
the cheese. Cook the uncooked pizza base and there you
have yourself a plain pizza.

524abf34-8744-44a4-adb9-091da778d463.title: Cooking tutor
524abf34-8744-44a4-adb9-091da778d463.text:
If you want to, you could add yourself a topping to the
pizza too. Why not try some anchovies?
